Game Architecture - Spring 2012


Homework 2 - Vector & Matrix, Cube Transformation
    Compiling:
        To build:
           $ cmake .
           $ make
           Ought to produce a hw1 binary in ./bin/ simply run that to get to the prompt. input is function name followed by any arguements separated by a space. help lists all available functions.

           If some of what I did seems strange, I was using some stuff specific to C++0x/C++11 (namely std::array and std::initializer_list) but decided to switch back to a more widely supported standard